{"tid":511266,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【後患無窮】電盈上訴得直　終院裁定通訊局多收牌費","createTime":"2017-12-27T10:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T13:38:14.000Z","uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"775f988a09c141b1f5f9b00afc0c640d30588736","tid":511266,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"電訊盈科（0008）前年入稟司法覆核，控告商經局局長和通訊局收取過多牌照費，終審法院裁定香港電訊（6823）上訴得直。通訊辦表示尊重法庭的裁決，會仔細研究判詞，由於裁決涉及公共財政，會與律政司商討，及按照財庫局政策指示作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n判詞指，政府錯誤理解《電訊條例》准許政府訂定牌照費用時，可以向牌照持有人收取稅收。而政府釐定牌費時將香港電訊的稅收及股息等利潤列入預算內，令通訊局收入超過法定目標收益，犯了法律上的錯誤。法庭認為，超收的牌費形同稅收。<br />\n<br />\n電盈入稟時又批評通訊局的營運基金，回報率遠高於開支所需。截至2008年止，基金滾存6.9億元，判詞認為基金產生的收益不應轉撥作政府一般收入。<br />\n<br />\n香港電訊發言人指歡迎法庭判決，「明顯地電訊業長久以來一直被收取過多的費用。」公司將研究判詞及考慮下一步的行動，或包括利用民事訴訟以取回多年來多付的費用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1514361111626&amp;issue=20171227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1514361111626%26issue%3D20171227&d=odruODfeFYMtT7fookMWeYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=36b9769d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1514361111626%26issue%3D20171227&h=c8541740\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1514361111626&amp;issue=20171227</a>"},{"pid":"34c712e5deed60cb889c980f6df2a26d3c7b158c","tid":511266,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"本來應該開係電訊台 廢事俾sales洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feec658c6fdd61a4c39790213439f583a1af5c40","tid":511266,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:14:53.000Z","msg":"有排告政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6249d72b27c34052332c25592a79ba90c1fb2018","tid":511266,"uid":26418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"會唔會開係時事台好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f972653683ab2651295cbd9df522221e95af54","tid":511266,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"顧客得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8e297888d8875ebd94ac61a14916b4eae37232","tid":511266,"uid":26418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f972653683ab2651295cbd9df522221e95af54","tid":511266,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"顧客得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bc71af94a97e99ca31e5cf317e4bbb5d35a062","tid":511266,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa1bfb980241dc01ef1d342b509055d24aee7964","tid":511266,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69f972653683ab2651295cbd9df522221e95af54","tid":511266,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"顧客得益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"無用，本來行政費條數就無18蚊一個月咁多"}]}